title: Permian Gearing Up For Abilene High
text:
Permian Gearing Up For Abilene High Posted: jgordon@kwes.com 
The Permian Panthers opened up district in impressive fashion last Friday. 
Mojo easily took down Midland Lee with a 45-0 win to earn their first district victory of the season. 
Permian has been dominant on their way to a 6-0 record this season. Everyone knows about the high flying offense, but the defense has been lights out as well. 
This week a very good abilene high team comes to Ratliff Stadium and the Panthers know that this game could have huge ramifications later on in District 3-6A 
Physical Address: 11320 West County Road 127 Midland, Texas, 79711
